==English==
===Adjective===
'''militant'''
# believing strongly in something
# [[aggressive]] or [[combative]]
# [[fighting]] or [[warlike]]; [[belligerent]]

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''militant'''
# someone who believes strongly in something (e.g. militant atheist)
# someone who campaigns for radical social, political or philosophical change
# an aggressive or fighting person (e.g. Islamic militant)
# one who serves as a [[soldier]]

